 Z‚ÜêFPS MAKEVIDEO DIR;N;CMD;R
‚çù Convert SVG frames to mp4 video
‚çù FPS: frames per second
‚çù DIR: directory containing frame_NNNNN.svg files
‚çù Returns path to output mp4 (empty string on error)

‚çù Count frames
 R‚Üê‚éïSHELL 'ls -1 ',DIR,'/frame_*.svg 2>/dev/null | wc -l'
 N‚Üê‚äÉ2‚äÉ‚éïVFI(‚àä‚äÉR)~' '
 :If N=0
   ‚éï‚Üê'No SVG frames found in ',DIR
   Z‚Üê''
   :Return
 :EndIf

‚çù Convert SVGs to PNGs (parallel)
 ‚éï‚Üê'Converting ',(‚çïN),' SVGs to PNGs...'
 CMD‚Üê'ls -1 ',DIR,'/frame_*.svg | xargs -P 8 -I {} sh -c ''f="{}"; rsvg-convert -w 2320 "$f" -o "${f%.svg}.png"'''
 R‚Üê‚éïSHELL CMD
 :If 0‚âÝ3‚äÉR
   ‚éï‚Üê'Error converting SVGs: ',‚àä‚äÉR
   Z‚Üê''
   :Return
 :EndIf

‚çù Encode mp4
 ‚éï‚Üê'Encoding mp4 at ',(‚çïFPS),' fps...'
 Z‚ÜêDIR,'/animation.mp4'
 CMD‚Üê'ffmpeg -y -framerate ',(‚çïFPS),' -i ',DIR,'/frame_%05d.png'
 CMD,‚Üê' -c:v libx264 -pix_fmt yuv420p'
 CMD,‚Üê' -vf "pad=ceil(iw/2)*2:ceil(ih/2)*2"'
 CMD,‚Üê' ',Z
 R‚Üê‚éïSHELL CMD
 :If 0‚âÝ3‚äÉR
   ‚éï‚Üê'Error encoding video'
   Z‚Üê''
   :Return
 :EndIf

 ‚éï‚Üê'Video written to ',Z
